@startuml
title Activity Diagram - Enroll in Course 

start

note right
Steps:
1. Student opens course catalog
2. System displays available courses
3. Student selects a course
4. System checks eligibility/capacity
5. If allowed, system creates enrollment
6. System shows confirmation OR cannot-enroll message
end note

:Open Course Catalog;
:Display Available Courses;
:Select Course;
:Check Eligibility and Capacity;

if (Allowed to enroll?) then (Yes)
  :Create Enrollment;
  :Show Enrollment Confirmation;
else (No)
  :Show Cannot Enroll Message;
endif

stop
@enduml
